spec: remove the winston logging and just use the standard nestjs logging
commitMessage:
Removed winston logging in favor of NestJS built-in logger

- Removed winston and winston-daily-rotate-file dependencies
- Deleted LoggingModule and LoggingService
- Updated DatabaseService and MonitoringService to use NestJS Logger
- Configured NestJS logger in main.ts
- Removed LoggingModule from AppModule
